1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,340
[Episode 38]

2
00:00:03,430 --> 00:00:05,190
Alright, I'll go out first.

3
00:00:12,630 --> 00:00:16,910
-You said it's your car.
-Isn't this Fuzhi's car?

4
00:00:18,190 --> 00:00:20,310
Never mind. I'll handle it myself.

5
00:00:28,190 --> 00:00:32,590
But do you really want to do this here?
There are a lot of people around.

6
00:00:35,310 --> 00:00:37,550
Don't worry. Nobody's here.

7
00:00:44,070 --> 00:00:48,950
Um, Fuzhi has been following you, right?

8
00:00:50,550 --> 00:00:52,030
He's just a driver.

9
00:00:57,700 --> 00:01:00,110
Does he watch over you like this every day?

10
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:04,790
If you don't want this,
I'll go call Fuzhi.

11
00:01:08,550 --> 00:01:10,350
Go ahead and call him if you dare.

12
00:01:38,820 --> 00:01:41,220
[To Be Continued]
